casebody.data:
Linda Lou DuBois v. James Rene DuBois (5584)

Borden, Bieluch and O’Connell, Js.

Submitted on briefs November 13 — decision released November 27, 1987 Bruce A. Fontanella filed a brief for the appellant (plaintiff). William J. Tracy, Jr., and William J. Eddy filed a brief for the appellee (defendant). Per Curiam.

We have thoroughly reviewed the records and briefs filed in this matter and, having afforded the plaintiffs claims of error the appropriate scope of review, we conclude that there is no merit to those claims.

There is no error.
